<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="brush-v">brush <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /brʌʃ/    美 /brʌʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>刷；擦：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Brush your teeth / shoes.
刷牙/刷刷你的鞋子。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They use small brooms to <strong>brush off</strong> snow caught in tiny holes.
他们用小扫帚扫去落到小洞里的雪。</p><footer> 2008 湖南</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>擦过；掠过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The light wind gently brushed my cheeks. 
微风轻拂着我的面颊。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>brushed past / by</strong> me in the street. 
他和我在街上擦肩而过。</p></div></div>